title: Spellblade Pack
description: This league supporter pack includes 250 Points, the Spellblade Supporter Forum Title, Spellblade Portrait Frame, Heist League Digital Soundtrack and the Spellblade Character Effect which has a visual charge-up as you slay monsters.
